        "CustomApp",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomSdk",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那CustomSdk是充当桥梁的角色吗？它同时连接边缘节点侧和执行器控制器侧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CustomSdk是核心枢纽。它部署在边缘节点上，但通过HTTP协议与远端的CustomApi交互。CustomApi运行在IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "HTTP connection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我把CustomCli、CustomApp、CustomLib都标注为IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode的组件，CustomApi和CustomSdk标注为IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController相关？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomSdk",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，CustomSdk虽然和CustomApi通信，但它物理上部署在边缘节点，应该标注为IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode。只有CustomApi属于执行器控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，CustomSdk是边缘节点的代理组件。那依赖关系上，CustomCli和CustomApp都使用CustomSdk？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomSdk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，而且它们都依赖CustomLib作为基础库。另外CustomSdk本身也依赖CustomLib。这是一个分层结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
