      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：CustomCli .. CustomLib : using，CustomSdk .. CustomLib : using，CustomApp .. CustomLib : using。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "通信语义需要明确。CustomSdk向CustomApi发送的是bRequest消息，承载在IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream上。返回的是bResponse消息，目标回到边缘节点。",
